description:
#Coronavirus has changed our way of life. What will it look like when we start integrating back into society? Will we be more #grateful? Will we experience feelings we ignored while away? What does this return to “normal” look like? 

In this ANN In-Depth episode, we talk with Dr. Peter Landless, Director of Health Ministries for the Seventh-day Adventist Church. You can learn more about Health Ministries at their website: https://healthministries.com/
